data.description: If you are looking for a country retreat away from the city life, look no further! This stunning 3-bedroom 2-bath brick home in Union County was built in 2002 and sits on 5 acres in Oak Grove Subdivision! When walking through the front door you are greeted with vaulted ceilings and a spacious family room with a fireplace, giving both a roomy yet cozy feel. Inside you will find a spacious floorplan and high-end finishes throughout. The kitchen and dining combo overlooks a picturesque landscape. Come get cozy on the large back porch and enjoy your peaceful oasis. This house will not last long as it is centrally located only 30 minutes from both Lake City and Gainesville. Don't miss out!
